description: A legendary speed demon owned by a member of the infamous Mid Night Club. After taking the car to ABR Hosoki Engineering for a complete reconstruction, the car came out with over 600hp under the hood, a part combination selected specifically for maintaining maximum velocity at Japanese highways and the capability of lapping Route C1 in less than 5 minutes. It's the main source of inspiration for the S30 Devil Z in Wangan Midnight.
creator: Keanny
